How is my personal
data used for refunds?
As we do not collect
the data when you make in-app purchases within our Game directly, in order to
better process you refund requests we have to obtain your consent for this data
collection and processing as well as for transfer thereof to our payment’s
agents.
Please be aware that
you are allowed to freely withdraw your consent for this purpose at any time,
but we note that in case of your consent withdrawal, we may be unable to
process your payments requests properly.
