How is my personal data used for
advertising?
To keep our Game free,
we display ads in it with the help of third-party advertising partners ("
Advertising
Partners
"). We integrate their technologies into our Game, thanks to
which Advertising partners independently determine which ads to show to you.
a.
Do Advertising partners collect my personal data?
In order to serve you
ads that may be of interest to you ("Targeted Advertising"),
Advertising Partners collect and use your Advertising ID, Location Information,
and Device Information. If location services are enabled in your Device
settings, Advertising partners may additionally collect data about your
geolocation.
In some cases,
Advertising Partners collect information about you on our behalf and act as a
processor of your personal data, and in some cases, Advertising Partners
independently decide to collect your personal data through the mechanisms built
into our applications. In the latter case, Advertising Partners act as a
controller in accordance with the EU General Data Protection Regulations
(GDPR).
