b.
How to opt-out of receiving Targeted Ads?
If you do not want to
receive Targeted Advertising on your mobile Device, you may opt-out when we
first ask you for permission to serve such advertising. In addition, your
Device may include an option to opt-out of receiving Targeted Advertising
across all applications on your Device. In addition, you may opt out of
receiving Targeted Advertising from a particular Advertising Partner. Please review
our list of advertising partners listed in paragraph a to learn how you can opt
out of receiving Targeted Advertising from a particular Advertising Partner.
In any case, you may
contact us at privacy@axlebolt.com and indicate your desire to opt out of
receiving Targeted Advertising. We will share this information with our
Advertising Partners.
Please note
that if you opt out of receiving Targeted
Advertising, you will still receive contextual advertising that is related to
the content of the Game you are playing.
How are
User’s Name
, User’s Avatar
and User’s ID used?
Our Game does not
require you to provide your real name or upload your own image. Having a
User’s Name and User’s Avatar
is
required, but if you do not want to provide them, they will be generated
automatically. If you wish to personalize your account, you have the option of
providing us with a User’s Name yourself, unless it is already used by another
player in our Game. If you do this, we will process your User’s Name and User’s
Avatar, but you can delete or change them at any time. Also, to minimize the personal
data we process, we assign a User’s ID to your account.
How is the User's email used?
To ensure the security
of your account in the Game, as well as to prevent all types of illegal or
unauthorized use of your account, we ask you to use your email address when
registering for our Game. The User's email address may be required to log in to
the Game and verify or restore your account if something goes wrong. We will
also send you important notifications related to your use of our Game, as well
as information about potentially interesting marketing offers, if you have
agreed to receive such information.
Please note that if you
wish, you can log in using third-party resources that will transfer your data
related to a third-party resource to us. We recommend that you familiarize
yourself with the list of third-party resources and their privacy policies:
