How
is my data used to combat fraud?
It is important for us
that the user experience in our Game is fair and competitive. Our
Terms of Use
strictly
prohibit the use of third-party programs to gain an unauthorized gaming
advantage when using games, which may include mods, hacks, cheats, scripts,
bots, simulators and automation programs. To ensure fair play, we use
anti-fraud technologies, for example, anti-fraud programs that can
automatically make decisions to temporarily block your account based on the
information we receive about the User's device.
